 the company started marketing its product overseas one of the companys first overseas clients was a uk based international infrastructure firm in  in  the weizmann team established its own company to be later merged with aaa and joined by entrepreneurs ron zuckerman and shaul shani the company severed itself from the weizmann institute and was incorporated under its new name—sapiens by  sapiens had established a client base encompassing israel the united kingdom switzerland canada south africa germany and venezuela in  sapiens was registered as a public limited liability company in the netherlands antilles under the name sapiens international corporation nv in  sapiens latin american division entered the brazilian market in  shares of sapiens began trading on the nasdaq exchange the year  is considered the companys peak with  workers employed at  branches around the world and a market cap of us million during the second half of the  sapiens focused on developing a business rules technology emerge and legacy modernization products and services the company was highly successful in winning contracts for updating information systems to deal with the year  problem and to adapt systems to the changeover to the new single european currency the euro in  the companys annual revenues reached usd but declined in the following years refocusing on insurance softwareedit in  formula systems until then a minority shareholder acquired control over the then struggling company dan goldstein then chairman of the formula group assumed the role of chairman of sapiens and supervised its recovery the company decided to focus solely on developing software solution for the insurance industry in  sapiens acquired harcase a canadabased software company developer of policy administration suite for property and casualty insurance in  goldstein initiated and carried out a way corporate merger between sapiens and two subsidiaries of formula vision these two companies both also focused on insurance solutions fis formula insurance solutions and idit merged into sapiens to form a world leader in software for the insurance sector in march  sapiens acquired ibexi solutions an india based provider of insurance business and technology solutions in asia pacific in july  sapiens acquired insseco an insurance software provider in poland for  million productsedit sapiens alis  life pension  annuities insurance software sapiens idit  general insurance software solution sapiens rapidsure  property and casualty insurance software sapiens reinsurance software sapiens decision  business decision management solution bdms sapiens emerge business rules engine see alsoedit tsvi misinai silicon wadi list of israeli companies quoted on the nasdaq ta bluetech index referencesedit  spns income statement yahoo finance  retrieved  february    sapiens international corp nv spnso company profile reuters  retrieved  september  sapiens international corporation nv incorporated on april   is a global provider of software solutions for the insurance industry   spns profile yahoo finance  retrieved  september    sapiens international corporation market cap spns ycharts september  retrieved  september  sapiens international corporation market cap m   a b sadeh shuki  december  קוסם שמוכר רעיונות דרכו של שאול שני מהגונגל בברזיל למיליארדים בישראל wizard who sells ideas the path of shaul shani from the jungle of brazil to the billions in israel themarker in hebrew retrieved  september  ספיאנס הוקמה על בסיס רעיון של מדענים במכון ויצמן בשנות ה מחולל יישומים מערכת שהותקנה בעיקר במחשבי ענק ואיפשרה לכתוב תוכנה במהירות גדולה יחסית   lori aviva  march  אחים יקרים dear brothers themarker in hebrew retrieved  september  בצבא שירת מסיני בממרם יחידת המחשב בענף כוח אדם   morgenstern henry  may  tsvi misinai israel business today retrieved  september  within three months of becoming head of a weizmann institute project to find such a tool back in  tsvi misinai saw his idea first used   a b harel ezra mena