he free encyclopedia jump to navigation search sapiens international corporation nv holon azrieli center headquarters of sapiens type public traded as nasdaq spns tase spns industry computer software founded   years ago  founder tsvi misinai tuvi orbach shai sole headquarters holon israel services insurance solutions revenue us  million  operating income us  million  profit us  million  total assets us  million  number of employees  parent formula systems  ltd subsidiaries sapiens decision sapiens tech website wwwsapienscom footnotes  references  sapiens international corporation is a publicly traded company headquartered in israel that develops computer software solutions for the insurance industry its shares are traded on the nasdaq capital market and on the tel aviv stock exchange as of july  the company has  employees and a market cap of us million contents  history  refocusing on insurance software  products  see also  references  external links historyedit sapiens grew out of an initiative dubbed db undertaken by a group of scientists from the weizmann institute of science during the s to develop a novel objectoriented application generator for use with mainframe computers one of the driving forces behind the initiative was tsvi misinai a graduate of the technion who in  went on to spearhead the project he teamed up with shai sole shmuel timor and eli raban by the late s and early s the weizmann team partnered with a local israeli company aaa–advanced automated applications founded by tuvi orbach began marketing db to domestic large organizations  subsequently the company started marketing its product overseas one of the companys first overseas clients was a uk based international infrastructure firm in  in  the weizmann team established its own company to be later merged with aaa and joined by entrepreneurs ron zuckerman and shaul shani the company severed itself from the weizmann institute and was incorporated under its new name—sapiens by  sapiens had established a client base encompassing israel the united kingdom switzerland canada south africa germany and venezuela in  sapiens was registered as a public limited liability company in the netherlands antilles under the name sapiens international corporation nv in  sapiens latin american division entered the brazilian market in  shares of sapiens began trading on the nasdaq exchange the year  is considered the companys peak with  workers employed at  branches around the world and a market cap of us million during the second half of the  sapiens focused on developing a business rules technology emerge and legacy modernization products and services the company was highly successful in winning contracts for updating information systems to deal with the year  problem and to adapt systems to the changeover to the new single european currency the euro in  the companys annual revenues reached usd but declined in the following years refocusing on insurance softwareedit in  formula systems until then a minority shareholder acquired control over the then struggling company dan goldstein then chairman of the formula group assumed the role of chairman of sapiens and supervised its recovery the company decided to focus solely on developing software solution for the insurance industry in  sapiens acquired harcase a canadabased software company developer of policy administration suite for property and casualty insurance in  goldstein initiated and carried out a way corporate merger between sapiens and two subsidiaries of formula vision these two companies both also focused on insurance solutions fis formula insurance solutions and idit merged into sapiens to form a world leader in software for the insurance sector in march  sapiens acquired ibexi solutions an india based provider of insurance business and technology solutions in asia pacific in july  sapiens acquired insseco an insurance software provider in poland for  million productsedit sapiens alis  life pension  annuities insurance software sapiens idit  general insurance software solution sapiens rapidsure  property and casualty insurance software sapiens reinsurance software sapiens decision  business decision management solution bdms sapiens emerge business rules engine see alsoedit tsvi misinai silicon wadi list of israeli companies quoted on the nasdaq ta bluetech index referencesedit  spns income statement yahoo finance  retrieved  february    sapiens international corp nv spnso company profile reuters  retrieved  september  sapiens international corporation nv incorporated on april   is a global provider of software solutions for the insurance industry   spns profile yahoo finance  retrieved  september    sapiens international corporation market cap spns ycharts september  retrieved  september  sapiens international corporation market cap m   a b sadeh shuki  december  קוסם שמוכר רעיונות דרכו של שאול שני מהגונגל בברזיל למיליארדים בישראל wizard who sells ideas the path of shaul shani from the jungle of brazil to the billions in israel themarker in hebrew retrieved  september  ספיאנס הוקמה על בסיס רעיון של מדענים במכון ויצמן בשנות ה מחולל יישומים מערכת שהותקנה בעיקר במחשבי ענק ואיפשרה לכתוב תוכנה במהירות גדולה יחסית   lori aviva  march  אחים יקרים dear brothers themarker in hebrew retrieved  september  בצבא שירת מסיני בממרם יחידת המחשב בענף כוח אדם   morgenstern henry  may  tsvi misinai israel business today retrieved  september  within three months of becoming head of a weizmann institute project to find such a tool back in  tsvi misinai saw his idea first used   a b harel ezra menashe  יש בנו עוצמה רבה we have great power in hebrew israel pp –  – retrieved  september  המוצר הגיע לרמת שימוש מסחרית בארץ רק בסוף שנות השבעים ורק עשר שנים מאוחר יותר החלו המאמצים לשווקו בחוץלארץ   shimoni eli  october  מנכל סאפיינס הפורש שווי החברה יגדל פי  ב שנים sapiens ceo companys value will triple in  years ynet in hebrew retrieved  september  החברה שהוקמה על ידי קבוצת יזמים שפרשה ממכון ויצמן לפני  